data.text:
Complete Image Galleries are available for the Junior Bulle Expo National Holstein Show 2016 where Judge Marc Comtois selected Rogy Goldwyn Chardaia (1st 5Yr) from Frederic Liaudat as Champion Holstein. Full pictures and results provided by Cowsmo thanks to Junior Bulle Expo for sponsorship.

Junior Bulle Expo

The Junior Bulle Expo National Holstein Show 2016 will take place Decembe2nd at 8.00 at the Espace Gruyere in Bulle, Switzerland, with Marc Comtois, QC serving as the official judge. Cowsmo will be there, providing coverage thanks to Junior Bulle Expo. The Junior Bulle Expo will take place December 1st-3rd at the Espace Gruyere in Bulle, Switzerland, with Marc Comtois, QC serving as the official judge. Cowsmo will be there, providing coverage thanks to Junior Bulle –Expo.
